hans christian andersen 's the little mermaid ( アンデルセン童話 にんぎょ姫 anderusen dōwa ningyo hime , lit . " andersen 's fairy tales : princess mermaid " ) is a japanese anime film based on hans christian andersen 's eponymous fairy tale , released in 1975 by toei animation .   unlike the disney adaptation released 14 years later , this film is closer to andersen 's story , notably in its preservation of the original and tragic ending .   the two main protagonists are the youngest daughter of the royal merman family , marina , and her best friend fritz , an atlantic dolphin calf .   in japan , this film was shown in the toei manga matsuri ( toei cartoon festival ) in 1975 .   the film was later released in the united states , dubbed into english by g. g. communications , inc. and prima film , inc. , on september 8 , 1979 .